== 开掘 ==
1862年2月，成千上万的工人挖掘了110万立方米的土，终于将运河连接到了提姆萨湖。淡水一到达该地区，就有更多的工人被雇佣来修建苏伊士运河。运河也允许通过渡船在狭窄的道路上运输材料和食物。<ref name="Digging">{{cite book|last1=Karabell|first1=Zachary|title=Parting the Desert: The Creation of the Suez Canal|date=2003|publisher=A.A. Knopf|isbn=9780375408830|page=[https://archive.org/details/partingdesertcre00kara/page/172 172]|url=https://archive.org/details/partingdesertcre00kara|url-access=registration|quote=British servicemen, sweet water canal.|accessdate=19 November 2016}}</ref><ref name="Ferry">{{cite web|title=Photo of ferry in canal|url=http://www.suezcanalzone.com/pics18.html|website=Suez Canal Zone|accessdate=20 November 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408044807/http://www.suezcanalzone.com/pics18.html|archivedate=8 April 2016}}</ref>
== 卡萨斯森战役 ==
1882年8月28日，卡萨斯森战役在甜水运河附近展开。<ref name="Household Cavalry in Public Domain">{{cite book|last1=Arthur|first1=Sir George|title=The story of the Household Cavalry|date=1909|publisher=London,: A. Constable|pages=[https://archive.org/details/storyofhousehold02arthuoft/page/676 676]–679|url=https://archive.org/details/storyofhousehold02arthuoft |accessdate=21 November 2016}}</ref>
== 英埃战争 ==
不到100年后，运河<ref name="Map">{{cite web|last1=Woolley|first1=Richard (Dick)|title=Suez Canal Zone Map|url=http://www.suezcanalzone.com/czmap.html|website=Suez Canal Zone|accessdate=20 November 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102071632/http://www.suezcanalzone.com/czmap.html|archivedate=2 November 2016}}</ref>不再提供干净的淡水，而是令人不安地受到污染。20世纪50年代，当英国士兵驻扎在该地区时，一些人把这条运河称为露天下水道。英国皇家空军人员被建议避免接触水，并被警告说运河将是逃兵的终点。<ref name="Brotherhood">{{cite book|last1=Richards|first1=Colin|title=New Skeletons|date=November 3, 2012|publisher=Colin Archer-Richards|isbn=9781291925623|edition=2nd|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=PnYhBwAAQBAJ&q=British+servicemen%2C+sweet+water+canal&pg=PT244|accessdate=19 November 2016|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522210456/https://books.google.com/books?id=PnYhBwAAQBAJ&q=British+servicemen,+sweet+water+canal&pg=PT244|dead-url=no}}</ref>从1951年10月到1952年1月，当国家、埃及、抵抗运动和英国士兵之间的战争变得特别血腥时，一些被折磨和杀害的英国士兵的遗体最终被扔进了运河。<ref name="Reassessing" /><ref name="Fishing">{{cite web|last1=Delta|first1=Charlie|title=Photos of the Sweet Water Canal in the 1950s|url=http://www.suezcanalzone.com/picsnt.html|website=Suez Canal Zone|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161029232825/http://www.suezcanalzone.com/picsnt.html|archivedate=2016-10-29}}</ref><ref name="Soldier Biography">{{cite book|last1=Tait|first1=James H.|title=One Day At A Time: My Lfe And Times (Ch. 41 Service in Suez)|date=21 November 2012|publisher=AuthorHouse|isbn=9781456793029|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=j6BhK9NCBnoC&q=Sweet+Water+Canal&pg=PA175|accessdate=20 November 2016|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511022708/https://books.google.com/books?id=j6BhK9NCBnoC&q=Sweet+Water+Canal&pg=PA175|dead-url=no}}</ref>

